ation\nand shed light on the robustness of nonconvex optimization algorithms against\ncertain types of so-called monotone adversaries. Numerical simulations are\nperformed to illustrate our results.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 28 Sep 2018 15:24:54 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 20 Apr 2019 02:03:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-04-23"}
